metadata.name: Blind 1/25
metadata.description:
hey! i'm peter! made this song in my bedroom and thought it was pretty dope so i decided to put it out. web3 gets it first <3

i decided to start minting low-cost editions of my songs because i really want more than just one person to be able to collect my music & i want people to be able to collect my music at an affordable price. i am really striving to onboard new fans/collectors this year as i am building some really dope things (merch, airdrops, private shows, etc.) and i want everyone to be included. this is just the beginning.

all collectors will receive:
access to my private, collector's only, Telegram chat & Discord channel

owner of the 1/1 (https://zora.co/collections/zora/19187) will receive:
- master .wav file of the song
- mixed stems
- .png of artwork
- .mp4 of visualizer
- free ticket (+1) to one Peter Saputo headline show.

written by Peter Saputo and Tommy Allen
produced by Peter Saputo
mixed by Ben Zelico
mastered by ThC)o Quayle
